  id: tokipona
  title: toki pona
  author: char321
  description: "Changes the game language to toki pona (replacing English). Requires
    the matching toki pona manual: https://char3210.github.io/ktane-toki-pona-manual/\n\nSource:
    https://github.com/char3210/ktane-toki-pona\n\nTranslations are still incomplete!
    Contributions are welcome.\n\nCredits:\n- translations compiled from the mun pi
    ante toki event, coordination document & translators here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/14hmPb6b9SFlSt3W3J-Mau48GZI7Q7gnYnhxXrFpzQ74/edit?tab=t.0\r\n-
    Language Customizer mod inspired the implementation approach of this mod https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2412167243\n-
    custom bomb manual generation logic from Translated Modules mod https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=850186070)"
  version: 1.0
  outputFolder: build
  debugBuild: 1
  previewImage: {fileID: 0}
